GigBudget

GigBudget is a simple web-based budgeting application designed for gig workers to track income, expenses, and estimate weekly earnings using browser storage.

Features
User signup and login using LocalStorage
Add and track income and expenses
Weekly income forecast calculation
Multi-language interface support
Responsive and mobile-friendly design
Tech Stack
HTML
CSS
JavaScript (Vanilla JS)
Browser LocalStorage
Dependencies

No external libraries, frameworks, or modules are required; the application runs entirely on native browsertechnologies.

How to Run
Download or clone the repository
Open the project folder
Double-click the index.html file or open it in any web browser
Project Structure
index.html – main structure of the app
style.css – styling and layout
script.js – application logic
